cle/2020-04-19/edmond-baraffe-ancien-entraineur-du-touquet-est-decede Edmond Baraffe, ancien entra\u00eeneur du Touquet, est d\u00e9c\u00e9d\u00e9] {{in lang|fr}}</ref>\n*[[Peter Beard]], 82, American photographer.<ref>[https://people.com/human-interest/peter-beard-dead-at-82-after-being-reported-missing/ Famed Photographer Peter Beard Dead at 82: 'He Died Where He Lived: In Nature,' His Family Says]</ref> (body discovered on this date)\n*[[Cecil B\u00f8dker]], 93, Danish writer.<ref>[https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/kultur/forfatteren-cecil-boedker-er-doed Forfatteren Cecil B\u00f8dker er d\u00f8d] {{in lang|da}}</ref>\n*[[Noach Dear]], 66, American jurist, [[New York Supreme Court]] judge (since 2015), COVID-19.<ref>[https://nypost.com/2020/04/19/brooklyn-supreme-court-justice-noach-dear-dies-of-coronavirus/ Former City Councilman Noach Dear dies of coronavirus]</ref>\n*[[Terry Doran]], 83\u201384, British music manager ([[Grapefruit (band)|Grapefruit]]).<ref>[https://bestclassicbands.com/terry-doran-beatles-dead-4-19-20/ Beatles Associate Terry Doran Dies: Report]</ref>\n*[[\u00cdndio (footballer, born 1931)|\u00cdndio]], 89, Brazilian footballer ([[Clube de Regatas do Flamengo|Flamengo]], [[RCD Espanyol|Espanyol]], [[Brazil national football team|national team]]).<ref>[https://oglobo.globo.com/esportes/morre-indio-decimo-maior-artilheiro-da-historia-do-flamengo-24382140 Morre \u00cdndio, d\u00e9cimo maior artilheiro da hist\u00f3ria do Flamengo] {{in lang|pt}}</ref>\n*[[Sergio Onofre Jarpa]], 99, Chilean politician, [[Senate of Chile|Senator]] (1973, 1990\u20131994) and [[Ministry of the Interior and Public Security (Chile)|Minister of the Interior]] (1983\u20131985).<ref>[https://ellibero.cl/alerta/fallecio-el-ex-senador-sergio-onofre-jarpa-uno-de-los-fundadores-de-rn/ Falleci\u00f3 el ex senador Sergio Onofre Jarpa, uno de los fundadores de RN] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*[[Claude Lafortune]], 83, Canadian television presenter, sculptor and costume designer, COVID-19.<ref